cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD. 

This paper is about improving the generation behavior of deep learning models for open-domain dialogue response generation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves fine-tuning the model, which falls under the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with reducing undesirable behaviors, which could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
